expo.name: Yapp - Y Oslo
expo.description:
A DESIGN, TECH AND INNOVATION DRIVEN CONFERENCE FOR THOSE WHO WANT TO SHAPE THE FUTURE.

Y is a big conference in the heart of Oslo, Youngstorget, September 25th-27th. We will cover topics within customer experience, design, innovation and technology.

At Y you will learn how to find the right problems, design and build services to solve them. Also organize better and grow the services we build - and last but not least: have FUN and meet other cool geeks.

Y is for everyone involved in making products and services in companies and organizations. Innovation teams, designers, UXers, business developers, digital managers or whatever you may call yourself.

Get a full overview with the Y app. Read about our amazing speakers and collect your favoritt talks in a personalized schedule.
